@startuml Secuencia Play - Arquitectura Completa v2.0
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

title Sistema Completo - Flujo Play con Backend + WebSocket\n**Frontend (Flux) + Backend (REST + WebSocket)**

actor Usuario
participant "TransportControls\n(UI)" as Controls
participant "TeleprompterStore\n(MAESTRO)" as Store
participant "AutoScrollService" as Scroll
participant "SyncService" as Sync
participant "WebSocketClient\n(Socket.IO)" as WSClient
participant "ApiClient\n(HTTP)" as API
participant "WebSocketServer\n(Backend)" as WSServer
participant "MongoDB\n(Database)" as DB
participant "PreviewPanel\n(ESCLAVO)" as Preview
participant "TeleprompterWindow\n(ESCLAVO)" as Window

== Inicialización y Carga de Datos ==

Usuario -> Controls : App inicia
activate Controls

Controls -> API : GET /api/auth/me
activate API
API -> WSServer : HTTP Request
activate WSServer
WSServer -> DB : findById(userId)
activate DB
DB --> WSServer : User data
deactivate DB
WSServer --> API : 200 OK {user}
deactivate WSServer
API --> Controls : User authenticated
deactivate API

Controls -> API : GET /api/config
activate API
API -> WSServer : HTTP Request
activate WSServer
WSServer -> DB : Configuration.findOne({userId})
activate DB
DB --> WSServer : Config or create default
deactivate DB
WSServer --> API : 200 OK {config}
deactivate WSServer
API --> Store : Apply config to state
deactivate API

Controls -> API : GET /api/scripts?page=1&limit=20
activate API
API -> WSServer : HTTP Request
activate WSServer
WSServer -> DB : Script.find({userId, deletedAt: null})
activate DB
DB --> WSServer : Scripts array
deactivate DB
WSServer --> API : 200 OK {scripts, pagination}
deactivate WSServer
API --> Controls : Scripts loaded
deactivate API

' Conectar WebSocket
Controls -> WSClient : connect()
activate WSClient
WSClient -> WSServer : Socket.IO handshake
activate WSServer
WSServer -> WSServer : activeConnections.set(socketId)
WSServer --> WSClient : Connected (socketId)
deactivate WSServer

WSClient -> WSServer : emit('identify', {userId, role})
activate WSServer
WSServer -> WSServer : activeConnections.set(socketId, {userId, role})
WSServer --> WSClient : ACK
deactivate WSServer
deactivate WSClient

deactivate Controls

== Usuario Presiona Play ==

Usuario -> Controls : Click Play
activate Controls
Controls -> Store : dispatch(play())
deactivate Controls

activate Store
Store -> Store : state.isPlaying = true
Store -> Store : state.timestamp = Date.now()
Store -> Store : notifyListeners()

' Notificación a componentes suscritos
Store --> Preview : notify(newState)
activate Preview
Preview -> Preview : Re-render con isPlaying=true
deactivate Preview

' Iniciar auto-scroll
Store -> Scroll : start()
activate Scroll
Scroll -> Scroll : intervalId = setInterval(tick, 16ms)\n**60 FPS**

' Broadcast local (main window → popup)
Store -> Sync : broadcastState(state)
activate Sync

Sync -> Sync : command = {\n  type: 'PLAY',\n  timestamp: now,\n  sourceId: 'master',\n  payload: state\n}

Sync -> Window : postMessage(command, '*')
activate Window
Window -> Window : if (message.sourceId === 'master')\n  applyState(message.payload)
Window -> Window : setState({isPlaying: true})
Window -> Window : **NO inicia auto-scroll local**\n(solo escucha a maestro)
deactivate Window

deactivate Sync

' Broadcast WebSocket (a otros usuarios/dispositivos)
Store -> WSClient : emit('sync:teleprompter', state)
activate WSClient
WSClient -> WSServer : WebSocket message
activate WSServer
WSServer -> WSServer : broadcast.emit('sync:teleprompter', state)
note right of WSServer
  Broadcast a todos los clientes
  del mismo usuario/proyecto
  (usando Socket.IO rooms)
end note
WSServer --> WSClient : ACK
deactivate WSServer
deactivate WSClient

deactivate Store

== Auto-Scroll Loop (60 FPS) ==

loop Cada 16ms (60 FPS)
  Scroll -> Scroll : deltaTime = now - lastUpdate
  Scroll -> Scroll : increment = calculateIncrement(\n  deltaTime,\n  state.speed\n)
  
  note right of Scroll
    **CÁLCULO UNIFICADO:**
    increment = (speed / 60) * deltaTime
    
    Ejemplo con speed=1.0:
    - 60 FPS → ~0.0167 por frame
    - Scroll suave y predecible
    - Mismo cálculo para todos
  end note
  
  Scroll -> Store : setScrollPosition(\n  prev + increment\n)
  
  activate Store
  Store -> Store : state.scrollPosition += increment
  Store -> Store : state.timestamp = Date.now()
  Store -> Store : notifyListeners()
  
  ' Actualización local
  Store --> Preview : notify(newState)
  activate Preview
  Preview -> Preview : Apply scroll to DOM:\nref.scrollTop = scrollPosition
  Preview -> Preview : **FUNCIONA ✓**
  deactivate Preview
  
  ' Broadcast a esclavos locales (throttled cada 50ms)
  alt cada 50ms (throttle)
    Store -> Sync : broadcastState(state)
    activate Sync
    Sync -> Window : postMessage({\n  type: 'SET_SCROLL_POSITION',\n  payload: {scrollPosition}\n})
    activate Window
    Window -> Window : setState({scrollPosition})
    Window -> Window : ref.scrollTop = scrollPosition
    Window -> Window : **Sincronizado ✓**
    deactivate Window
    deactivate Sync
    
    ' Broadcast WebSocket (throttled cada 100ms)
    alt cada 100ms (throttle WebSocket)
      Store -> WSClient : emit('sync:teleprompter', {scrollPosition})
      activate WSClient
      WSClient -> WSServer : WebSocket update
      activate WSServer
      WSServer -> WSServer : broadcast to room
      deactivate WSServer
      deactivate WSClient
    end
  end
  
  deactivate Store
end

== Usuario Guarda Script (API Call) ==

Usuario -> Controls : Ctrl+S (save script)
activate Controls
Controls -> API : PUT /api/scripts/:id
activate API
API -> API : Add JWT token to headers\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>

API -> WSServer : HTTP PUT /api/scripts/:id\nBody: {title, content}
activate WSServer

WSServer -> WSServer : authenticateToken middleware
WSServer -> DB : Session.findOne({token, isActive: true})
activate DB
DB --> WSServer : Session valid
deactivate DB

WSServer -> DB : Script.findOneAndUpdate(\n  {_id, userId},\n  {title, content}\n)
activate DB
DB --> WSServer : Updated script
deactivate DB

WSServer -> DB : AuditLog.create({\n  entityType: 'Script',\n  action: 'update',\n  userId, changes\n})
activate DB
DB --> WSServer : Log created
deactivate DB

WSServer -> WSServer : io.emit('script:updated', script)
note right of WSServer
  Notifica a todos los clientes
  conectados que el script cambió
end note

WSServer --> API : 200 OK {script}
deactivate WSServer
API --> Controls : Script saved
deactivate API

' WebSocket notification recibida
WSClient <- WSServer : on('script:updated', script)
activate WSClient
WSClient -> Store : dispatch(updateScript(script))
activate Store
Store -> Store : Update script in state
Store -> Store : notifyListeners()
Store --> Preview : notify(newState)
activate Preview
Preview -> Preview : Refresh script in UI
deactivate Preview
deactivate Store
deactivate WSClient

Controls -> Controls : Show toast: "Script guardado"
deactivate Controls

== Cambio de Velocidad desde Popup (ESCLAVO → MAESTRO → API) ==

Window <- Usuario : Mouse wheel
activate Window
Window -> Window : newSpeed = speed ± 0.1
Window -> Sync : sendRequest({\n  type: 'REQUEST_SPEED_CHANGE',\n  payload: {speed: newSpeed},\n  sourceId: 'popup-123'\n})
deactivate Window

activate Sync
Sync -> Store : dispatch(setSpeed(newSpeed))
activate Store
Store -> Store : state.speed = validateSpeed(newSpeed)
Store -> Store : notifyListeners()

' Guardar en backend
Store -> API : PUT /api/config\nBody: {scrollSpeed: newSpeed}
activate API
API -> WSServer : HTTP PUT /api/config
activate WSServer
WSServer -> DB : Configuration.findOneAndUpdate(\n  {userId},\n  {scrollSpeed: newSpeed}\n)
activate DB
DB --> WSServer : Updated config
deactivate DB
WSServer --> API : 200 OK {config}
deactivate WSServer
API --> Store : Config saved
deactivate API

Store --> Preview : notify(newState)
activate Preview
Preview -> Preview : Actualiza UI (slider)
deactivate Preview

Store -> Sync : broadcastState(state)
Sync -> Window : postMessage({\n  type: 'SET_SPEED',\n  payload: {speed: newSpeed},\n  requestId: 'req-123',\n  ack: true\n})
activate Window
Window -> Window : setState({speed: newSpeed})
Window -> Window : **Confirmado ✓**
Window -> Sync : sendAck('req-123')
deactivate Window

' Broadcast WebSocket
Store -> WSClient : emit('sync:teleprompter', {speed: newSpeed})
activate WSClient
WSClient -> WSServer : WebSocket message
activate WSServer
WSServer -> WSServer : broadcast to room
deactivate WSServer
deactivate WSClient

deactivate Store
deactivate Sync

== Detección de Fin de Texto ==

Scroll -> Scroll : if (detectEndOfText())
activate Scroll
Scroll -> Scroll : **Calcula fin:**\nestimatedHeight = lines.length × lineHeight\nmaxScroll = estimatedHeight - viewportHeight

Scroll -> Store : dispatch(pause())
activate Store
Store -> Store : state.isPlaying = false
Store -> Store : notifyListeners()

Store --> Preview : notify(newState)
activate Preview
Preview -> Preview : Actualiza UI (botón Play)
deactivate Preview

Store -> Sync : broadcastState(state)
activate Sync
Sync -> Window : postMessage({type: 'PAUSE'})
activate Window
Window -> Window : setState({isPlaying: false})
deactivate Window
deactivate Sync

' Broadcast WebSocket
Store -> WSClient : emit('sync:teleprompter', {isPlaying: false})
activate WSClient
WSClient -> WSServer : WebSocket message
activate WSServer
WSServer -> WSServer : broadcast to room
deactivate WSServer
deactivate WSClient

' Auto-advance
Store -> Store : handleAutoAdvance()
Store -> Store : Busca siguiente script
Store -> Store : if (nextScript exists)\n  loadNextScript()\n  play()

deactivate Store
deactivate Scroll

note over Store, WSServer
  **VENTAJAS DE ARQUITECTURA COMPLETA:**
  
  ✓ Frontend: Flux pattern con stores centralizados
  ✓ Backend: RESTful API + WebSocket real-time
  ✓ Base de datos: Persistencia en MongoDB
  ✓ Sincronización multi-nivel:
    - Local: Main window ↔ Popup (postMessage)
    - Red: WebSocket para multi-usuario
    - Persistencia: API REST para CRUD
  ✓ Autenticación: JWT con refresh token
  ✓ Audit log: Todas las operaciones registradas
  ✓ Escalable: Agregar más clientes fácilmente
  ✓ Seguro: Rate limiting + validación + roles
end note

== Pausa desde Preview ==

Preview <- Usuario : Click Pause
activate Preview
Preview -> Store : dispatch(pause())
deactivate Preview

activate Store
Store -> Store : state.isPlaying = false
Store -> Scroll : stop()
activate Scroll
Scroll -> Scroll : clearInterval(intervalId)
Scroll -> Scroll : intervalId = null
deactivate Scroll

Store -> Store : notifyListeners()
Store --> Preview : notify(newState)

Store -> Sync : broadcastState(state)
activate Sync
Sync -> Window : postMessage({type: 'PAUSE'})
activate Window
Window -> Window : setState({isPlaying: false})
Window -> Window : **Todos sincronizados ✓**
deactivate Window
deactivate Sync

Store -> WSClient : emit('sync:teleprompter', {isPlaying: false})
activate WSClient
WSClient -> WSServer : WebSocket message
activate WSServer
WSServer -> WSServer : broadcast to room
deactivate WSServer
deactivate WSClient

deactivate Store

@enduml
